\"1. Recharge and pay 800 book beans, you
can activate the ad-free privilege and enjoy 30-day ad-free rights. 2. On the iOS platform,
only AppStore payment methods are available for purchase. You can go to the AppStore account
settings to select Alipay, WeChat, UnionPay and other payment methods. 3. The Android
platform recharges and pays 800 Shudou for purchase through the Novel Shudou Recharge
Center. 4. After purchase, you can read the whole novel without ads. The original paid
novels still need to be paid for. After purchase, ads are free for reading. 5. The ad-free
privilege will take effect immediately after the deduction is completed, and the validity
period is 30 days; if it does not take effect directly, please wait for 30 min, and do not
repeat the purchase within a short time. 6. The remaining validity period of the privilege
after purchase can be viewed in real time through the book introduction section above the
book detail page. 7. The ad-free privileges purchased through the AppStore recharge can not
be used in the non-iOS Baidu APP; the ad-free privileges purchased in the Android Shudou
recharge center cannot be used in the non-Android Baidu APP. 8. After this privilege is
activated, refunds are not supported, please understand. 9. This privilege does not support
Baidu to help you pay discounts and use book coupons. 10. If you have any questions about
other privilege purchases, please consult Baidu APP customer service. 11. To the extent
permitted by law, Baidu has the right to interpret this privileged product. \"

story_tab_month_tab_default_poem_Apr:
In April, the rain suddenly clears up, and
the weather in Nanshan becomes clear.
story_tab_month_tab_default_poem_Aug:
Tonight, when the moon shines brightly and
everyone looks around, I don’t know who is missing in autumn thoughts.
story_tab_month_tab_default_poem_Dec:
Suddenly a spring breeze comes overnight,
thousands of pear trees bloom
story_tab_month_tab_default_poem_Feb:
The grass is long and the orioles are flying
in the February sky, the willows are blowing on the embankment and are drunk with the spring
smoke
story_tab_month_tab_default_poem_Jan:
Everything in the spring mountain should be
good. How many peaks can you see the flowers in January?
story_tab_month_tab_default_poem_Jul:
The mist in the sky is faint and the moon is
shining in the sky. The autumn period of Yinhan and Han Dynasties are the same throughout
the ages.
story_tab_month_tab_default_poem_Jun:
The lotus leaves touching the sky are
infinitely green, and the lotus flowers reflecting the sun are uniquely red.
story_tab_month_tab_default_poem_Mar:
At dusk of March, the flowers fall and the
love becomes stronger
story_tab_month_tab_default_poem_May:
From time to time, I see sparse stars
falling on the painted eaves, and at a few oclock, small fireflies are flying
story_tab_month_tab_default_poem_Nov:
The fallen leaves of the sycamore tree are
dancing gracefully, and the weeping branches of the snowy willow are slowly rising.
story_tab_month_tab_default_poem_Oct:
Tasting the rice in the mountains means
knowing the good moon, looking for plum blossoms on the wild paths and seeing the spring.
story_tab_month_tab_default_poem_Sep:
After the new rain in the empty mountains,
the weather comes late in autumn

Our platform only provides programmatic advertising matching technology and will not obtain your behavior or personal data on the advertiser`s website or application. Programmatic advertising is a versatile, legal advertising technology. <b><b>If you are not interested in targeted advertising or programmatic advertising recommended and displayed by advertisers, you can set up to turn off "Personalized Ads" at any time here.
